modules.description: Reads AWS configuration files and parses them into Yojson values for programmatic access. Processes structured data such as JSON objects representing region, credentials, and service endpoints. Used to dynamically load and validate AWS settings in cloud-based applications.

Parses AWS configuration strings into structured key-value pairs and nested associations. Works with JSON-like data structures and provides direct access to S3-related configuration values. Reads and extracts specific credentials or config values from files or in-memory data.
